## Description
_Creates a stream of frost in the direction you are pointing which slows and continually damages targets._

Frost ray deals 3 damage per second and applies Frostbite effect for 10 seconds.

## Trivia
- Frost ray has a range of 17 blocks
- The damage of the spell increases to 4 damage per second while using Appretice or Advanced Ice wand and 5 damage per second while using Master Ice wand.
- Whith activated Ring Of Glaciation you can achieve 6 damage per second while using Advanced or Master Ice wand - this is the highest damage you can achieve.
